Package: siduction-art-gdm-desperado
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    gdm
Description: GDM theme for siduction 12.1 release
 release specific artwork theme for the GDM display manager to be used in
 combination GTK2 based desktop environments like Xfce or LXDE.
 .
 GDM artwork for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-kde-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-kde-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    siduction-art-ksplash-desperado,
    siduction-art-kdm-desperado
Recommends: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado,
    dmz-cursor-theme
Description: KDE theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific metapackage depending on ksplash, kdm and KDE themes to be
 used in combination with the K Desktop Environment. This package also
 provides a release specific color scheme for KDE.
 .
 KDE artwork metapackage for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)

