Package: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-wallpaper-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: siduction wallpaper for the 12.1 release
 release specific wallpapers, compatible with the K Desktop Environment, Xfce,
 LXDE and GNOME.
 .
 Wallpapers for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-xfce-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-xfce-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    siduction-art-xsplash-desperado
Recommends: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado,
    dmz-cursor-theme
Description: Xfce theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific metapackage depending on xfce4-session, gdm3 and Xfce themes
 to be used in combination with the Xfce desktop environment.
 .
 Xfce artwork metapackage for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)

